location.fullValue: Hummingbird Bonus Room 1 Plan, Broadmoore Heights

data.description: You're going to love this beautiful gated Belmar North community nestled beside the renowned Belmar Golf Club in North Norman (Moore Public Schools). Location can not be beat, just a stones throw to HWY 77 for easy access to OKC and Tinker AFB. This home has all the space you could want! 3 beds + 3 baths + study downstairs AND a bonus room (could be 4th bedroom) + half bath upstairs. You will love every inch of this beauty starting with the tasteful landscaping and immaculately kept yard. Stepping inside you are greeted with gorgeous oversized tile in the welcoming entry. The entry opens into a lovely great room living/dining/kitchen. The sellers just replaced the flooring in the living room with gorgeous luxury vinyl planks, a dream for durability and maintenance. The corner fireplace is a beautiful focal point, and sits beside two large windows overlooking the spacious back yard. The U-shaped kitchen is as functional as it is beautiful. It features ample painted/glazed cabinetry, stainless steel built-in appliances, lovely accent lighting, stone tile backsplash, and stone counters. The primary bedroom is a wonderful size and features a lovely ensuite bathroom complete with dual sinks and a separate tub and shower. The private backyard is a blank slate for all the entertaining you can dream up. Game day barbecues? Birthday party shenanigans? Slip and slide and popsicles? Backyard campout? The possibilities are endless. Bonus, some fresh touch up painting has also been done throughout. Come and check it out!
